===Usage note===
'''Zap''' is colloquial in all senses.

===Noun===
'''zap''' (''plural'' '''zaps''')

#A sound made by a sudden release of [[electricity]] or some similar [[energy]].
#An electrical shock.
#:''You might feel a little zap touching a metal doorknob when the air is dry.''

